## Naming Conventions

| Thing | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Components | PascalCase | `BriefCard`, `InterviewRoom` |
| Hooks | camelCase + use prefix | `useBrief`, `useCredits` |
| Convex functions | camelCase | `createBrief`, `listInterviews` |
| API routes | kebab-case folders | `/api/hubspot-callback` |
| Constants | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE | `CREDIT_COST_PER_MINUTE` |
| Types/Interfaces | PascalCase | `Brief`, `InterviewSession` |
| Env vars | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE | `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY` |

