## Commit Convention

```
feat: add dynamic follow-up question generation
fix: correct credit deduction race condition
chore: update Convex schema for draft status
refactor: extract HubSpot content mapper to lib
docs: update architecture with R2 storage flow
```

---

## What NOT to Do

- ❌ Never expose API keys client-side
- ❌ Never call external APIs directly from Convex functions (use HTTP actions instead)
- ❌ Never store audio blobs in Convex — use Cloudflare R2
- ❌ Never bypass credit checks — always deduct via `internalMutation`
- ❌ Never use `router.refresh()` when a Convex `useQuery` reactive subscription will do
- ❌ Never hardcode HubSpot portal IDs or content IDs
